node.detail_zh: 患者為待業印尼籍外傭，最近無外遊記錄，8 月 4 日出現症狀。患者 7 月 23 日開始居於荃灣享和街 74 號地下的張大偉僱傭中心，期間主要留在僱傭中心及到附近街市。
node.detail_en: The patient is an Indonesian domestic helper awaiting employment, with no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on August 4. She began staying at David Cheung Employment Agency at 74 Heung Wo Street on July 23, and mainly stayed at the Agency and visited markets nearby.
